rem Hosaka Lobby
rem 8/21/2017

do Examine Lobby
 [
  ifflag hosaka alarm
   [
    print The alarm sounds even louder in this open space. Most of the employees have
    print made it out. If any are left, they'll have to deal with corporate security.
   |
    print It's a sparse space, but with room enough for a reception desk. Behind the 
    print desk a secretary tries to busy herself, avoiding eye contact with the hired
    print help. The employees don't seem to mind.
   ]
 ]

do Walk East
 [
  ifflag hosaka alarm
   [
    print You need to get out of here before corporate security shows up.
   |
    print You follow some employees and move deeper into the complex, coming to a
    print junction.
    go Hosaka Junction
   ]
 ]

do Exit Building
 [
  ifflag hosaka alarm
   [
    print You step outside into the chaos, people shuffle around not knowing where
    print to go. You take advantage of the confussion slipping past security.
    setflag hosaka exit
   |
    print You walk out the door as another group of people are leaving.
   ]
  go Outside Hosaka
 ]


